576
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:30,850
The exhibits are in the bag.

577
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:37,820
Mr. Li, you're neither the client

578
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:39,460
nor the lawyer.

579
00:21:39,730 --> 00:21:40,700
I don't think you should hold it.

580
00:21:42,250 --> 00:21:42,940
Lu Xun,

581
00:21:44,370 --> 00:21:45,580
before I congratulate you

582
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,060
on becoming the secondary partner
of Zhanying,

583
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,130
here we meet already.

584
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:50,660
I hear the plaintiff Fang Ruomei

585
00:21:51,090 --> 00:21:52,330
has also come to this party.

586
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:54,490
I guess I should come, too.

587
00:21:55,130 --> 00:21:56,730
Shouldn't I?

588
00:21:56,730 --> 00:21:57,700
Don't say that.

589
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:58,900
I'll just hold my own bag.

590
00:21:59,300 --> 00:22:00,700
How can I have my boss hold it for me?

591
00:22:01,130 --> 00:22:02,060
Feel free to talk.

592
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:03,010
Fine.

593
00:22:03,850 --> 00:22:04,820
Your tie...

594
00:22:05,490 --> 00:22:06,420
As you know,

595
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:07,610
my paralegal

596
00:22:07,610 --> 00:22:09,130
usually helps me wear a tie.

597
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:12,610
But since this morning,

598
00:22:12,610 --> 00:22:14,250
she has been so busy

599
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:16,900
that she didn't even go to the firm.

600
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:18,370
I'm quite helpless, aren't I?

601
00:22:26,010 --> 00:22:26,850
I hear the case

602
00:22:26,850 --> 00:22:27,660
between Morris and Ruomei

603
00:22:27,660 --> 00:22:28,900
will have the first trial soon.

604
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:31,700
Mr. Lu, you look quite peaceful.

605
00:22:32,370 --> 00:22:33,820
You must be certain to win.

606
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,540
That's for sure.

607
00:22:37,250 --> 00:22:37,970
For this case,

608
00:22:38,730 --> 00:22:40,250
I've acquired

609
00:22:40,250 --> 00:22:41,370
very clear facts

610
00:22:41,370 --> 00:22:43,300
and chains of evidence.

611
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:46,090
I pick lawsuits under conditions.

612
00:22:46,090 --> 00:22:47,730
I'm different from you.

613
00:22:48,730 --> 00:22:49,780
I pick cases upon people.

614
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:51,820
Right.

615
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:54,700
Regardless of right or wrong,

616
00:22:54,700 --> 00:22:56,300
both parties have the right to safeguard

617
00:22:56,300 --> 00:22:58,330
their legitimate interests with laws.

618
00:22:58,940 --> 00:22:59,780
This is the first lesson

619
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:00,850
we've learned.

620
00:23:01,130 --> 00:23:02,210
Every lawyer

621
00:23:02,210 --> 00:23:03,730
wants to be a chivalrous knight,

622
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:04,970
but...

623
00:23:06,010 --> 00:23:06,660
Who would care

624
00:23:07,010 --> 00:23:09,580
about legal directors like us?

625
00:23:09,580 --> 00:23:09,940
Right?

626
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:11,580
Well,

627
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:13,010
are you hungry, Boss?

628
00:23:13,180 --> 00:23:14,610
I hear when someone is hungry,

629
00:23:14,610 --> 00:23:16,300
he'll easily feel upset.

630
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,820
Would you like to stop talking

631
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:18,370
and...

632
00:23:18,370 --> 00:23:19,010
And have something to eat?

633
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:25,130
That is

634
00:23:25,130 --> 00:23:27,780
Lan He,

635
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:28,580
the daughter of the founder of AES

636
00:23:28,580 --> 00:23:29,300
and the present CEO.

637
00:23:29,970 --> 00:23:31,010
After she finished her work,

638
00:23:31,300 --> 00:23:32,090
she came back to China

639
00:23:32,090 --> 00:23:33,330
with Li Chongwen.

640
00:23:37,210 --> 00:23:38,970
After being away from my motherland
for four years,

641
00:23:38,970 --> 00:23:40,130
I'm finally back.

642
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:41,850
All present tonight

643
00:23:41,850 --> 00:23:44,210
are old friends of AES.

644
00:23:44,210 --> 00:23:45,460
I'd like to

645
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:46,490
thank you.

646
00:23:51,330 --> 00:23:51,820
Tonight,

647
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:52,970
I'm going to tell you

648
00:23:52,970 --> 00:23:53,700
some good news.

649
00:23:54,210 --> 00:23:55,780
We have

650
00:23:55,780 --> 00:23:57,610
successfully merged

651
00:23:57,610 --> 00:23:59,700
the new game company,

652
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:00,700
Ruomei.

653
00:24:01,850 --> 00:24:03,250
It also

654
00:24:03,250 --> 00:24:04,940
makes up for our weak points

655
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:07,580
in the gaming industry.

656
00:24:08,090 --> 00:24:08,900
Now,

657
00:24:08,900 --> 00:24:09,970
you may have some confusion.

658
00:24:09,970 --> 00:24:11,180
Recently,

659
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:12,900
Ruomei just

660
00:24:12,900 --> 00:24:14,900
sued Morris

661
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:17,090
for plagiarism and infringement.

662
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:19,700
I've found the best advisor

663
00:24:19,700 --> 00:24:21,540
for Ruomei.

664
00:24:21,540 --> 00:24:22,940
He's Mr. Li Chongwen,

665
00:24:22,940 --> 00:24:25,130
the new legal director

666
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:26,420
of AES.

667
00:24:37,490 --> 00:24:39,060
Nice to meet you, everyone.

668
00:24:45,090 --> 00:24:46,850
You know what?

669
00:24:47,580 --> 00:24:48,780
Tonight,

670
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:51,580
the lawyers for Morris,

671
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:54,250
who are juniors of Chongwen,

672
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:56,010
have also come.

673
00:24:56,010 --> 00:24:57,780
They try to be nice, I guess.

674
00:24:59,060 --> 00:25:00,090
If Morris

675
00:25:00,090 --> 00:25:01,660
apologizes in public

676
00:25:01,820 --> 00:25:02,490
and sells

677
00:25:02,490 --> 00:25:04,060
2% of the shares,

678
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:06,090
we don't need

679
00:25:06,090 --> 00:25:07,180
to go to court.

680
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:08,660
What do you think, Mr. Lu and Miss Qian?

681
00:25:10,130 --> 00:25:11,010
AES has barely lost

682
00:25:11,010 --> 00:25:12,130
even a single case.

683
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:13,210
Yeah.

684
00:25:14,460 --> 00:25:15,610
Why have lawyers of Zhanying

685
00:25:15,610 --> 00:25:16,370
come to this party?

686
00:25:16,700 --> 00:25:18,300
Yeah. Why did they come?

687
00:25:24,700 --> 00:25:25,580
I'm your boss.

688
00:25:26,850 --> 00:25:27,370
I'll take care of this.

689
00:25:33,900 --> 00:25:35,060
Hello, everybody.

690
00:25:35,060 --> 00:25:36,420
I'm Lu Xun,

691
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:37,540
the chief lawyer

692
00:25:38,420 --> 00:25:39,010
for the Morris case.

693
00:25:40,210 --> 00:25:41,420
Five years ago,

694
00:25:41,420 --> 00:25:43,580
Ruomei launched its first game.

695
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,300
Because of excessive imitation,

696
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:47,660
Ruomei was accused of plagiarism
by overseas companies.

697
00:25:48,060 --> 00:25:49,610
In the past five years,

698
00:25:49,610 --> 00:25:52,370
Ruomei has been sued again and again.

699
00:25:52,370 --> 00:25:54,130
It became more and more famous instead.

700
00:25:54,130 --> 00:25:55,300
It launched games

701
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:56,580
faster and faster.

702
00:25:59,490 --> 00:26:00,700
But this time,

703
00:26:01,660 --> 00:26:03,420
Ruomei accused
someone else of plagiarism.

704
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:05,330
I'm not surprised, though.

705
00:26:05,610 --> 00:26:06,940
Because the founder of Ruomei

706
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:07,820
once said something

707
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:08,900
like this.

708
00:26:09,370 --> 00:26:10,130
"Imitation is

709
00:26:11,010 --> 00:26:13,130
for better progress."

710
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:16,010
How shameless!

711
00:26:18,010 --> 00:26:18,700
Lu Xun,

712
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:20,780
you're making a slander.

713
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,900
You can try

714
00:26:23,210 --> 00:26:24,820
sending a lawyer's letter to me.

715
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:26,730
I take over

716
00:26:26,730 --> 00:26:28,010
every lawsuit

717
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:30,010
with a clear conscience.

718
00:26:30,540 --> 00:26:32,250
And I have never lost

719
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,130
even a single case.

720
00:26:36,370 --> 00:26:37,130
This time,

721
00:26:39,330 --> 00:26:40,130
I won't lose, either.

722
00:27:00,090 --> 00:27:01,010
You said

723
00:27:01,010 --> 00:27:02,610
that my interests always come first.

724
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,250
I also said

725
00:27:04,900 --> 00:27:06,210
no matter what you do,

726
00:27:06,210 --> 00:27:07,580
you mustn't get her involved.

727
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:11,760
(AES Fusion Welcome Celebration 9:05 PM)

728
00:27:11,780 --> 00:27:12,370
(AES Fusion Welcome Celebration 9:05 PM)
Qian Wei!

729
00:27:12,370 --> 00:27:16,800
(AES Fusion Welcome Celebration 9:05 PM)

730
00:27:16,820 --> 00:27:18,210
This is between Qian Wei and me.

731
00:27:19,060 --> 00:27:20,210
Let go of her.

732
00:27:20,210 --> 00:27:22,600
(Fusion Welcome Celebration)

733
00:27:23,490 --> 00:27:24,460
I'm her boss.

734
00:27:30,540 --> 00:27:31,490
Give me two minutes.

735
00:27:43,900 --> 00:27:44,610
What happened tonight was

736
00:27:44,610 --> 00:27:45,490
quite unexpected.

737
00:27:46,370 --> 00:27:47,330
I only planned

738
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:49,090
to have you celebrate my promotion.

739
00:27:49,330 --> 00:27:50,780
I didn't know Lu Xun would come.

740
00:27:51,730 --> 00:27:53,060
He enraged Lan He

741
00:27:53,060 --> 00:27:53,610
so that

742
00:27:53,610 --> 00:27:54,370
she blurted out

743
00:27:54,370 --> 00:27:55,580
all the things.

744
00:27:56,130 --> 00:27:56,660
Lan He and I are

745
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:57,820
only colleagues.

746
00:28:00,850 --> 00:28:02,580
Considering the value of Ruomei,

747
00:28:03,700 --> 00:28:05,370
AES's acquisition plan

748
00:28:06,130 --> 00:28:07,300
must have started

749
00:28:07,300 --> 00:28:08,700
two years ago.

750
00:28:13,370 --> 00:28:15,090
I called you every week.

751
00:28:16,490 --> 00:28:17,010
And you knew

752
00:28:17,010 --> 00:28:18,700
I was working on the Morris case.

753
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:21,060
But you never told me

754
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:23,490
that you were giving advice to Ruomei.

755
00:28:27,090 --> 00:28:28,300
I thought you contacted me

756
00:28:28,300 --> 00:28:29,780
because you cared for our relationship.

757
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:32,610
But actually,

758
00:28:32,610 --> 00:28:34,250
you were just fishing
for information, huh?

759
00:28:35,610 --> 00:28:36,370
Oh, I understand.

760
00:28:38,090 --> 00:28:39,540
No wonder

761
00:28:39,540 --> 00:28:40,780
Ruomei managed to know

762
00:28:40,780 --> 00:28:41,490
all the strategies

763
00:28:41,490 --> 00:28:43,010
and chains of evidence we had.

764
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:47,660
We?

765
00:28:48,730 --> 00:28:50,010
Do you mean you and Lu Xun?

766
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:01,180
"We" should refer to you and me.

767
00:29:02,610 --> 00:29:03,250
Over the years,

768
00:29:03,250 --> 00:29:04,010
I've been working so hard.

769
00:29:04,010 --> 00:29:04,850
Why?

770
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:07,820
Just to be with you.

771
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:09,250
Now I've realized my dream.

772
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:10,130
I'm back to you.

773
00:29:10,130 --> 00:29:10,940
Isn't it enough for you?

774
00:29:15,090 --> 00:29:16,130
You have used me

775
00:29:16,130 --> 00:29:17,010
in such a terrible way.

776
00:29:17,010 --> 00:29:18,210
Why can you still

777
00:29:18,210 --> 00:29:19,490
talk about our relationship?

778
00:29:21,180 --> 00:29:22,940
Director Li, let me ask you something.

779
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:25,540
If the evidence I have

780
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:26,300
can help you

781
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:27,420
win the case,

782
00:29:27,420 --> 00:29:28,580
what will Ms. Lan give you?

783
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:30,900
Will she make you succeed,

784
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:31,940
get famous

785
00:29:32,460 --> 00:29:33,970
and realize your so-called dream?

786
00:29:36,420 --> 00:29:37,460
Say something!

787
00:29:39,210 --> 00:29:40,940
I'm the legal director of AES.

788
00:29:41,850 --> 00:29:43,820
I can't decide

789
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:44,660
what company it acquires.

790
00:29:45,580 --> 00:29:46,700
In my mind,

791
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:48,090
I'm thinking about nothing,

792
00:29:48,090 --> 00:29:49,210
but how to make you

793
00:29:49,210 --> 00:29:49,970
live a good life

794
00:29:49,970 --> 00:29:50,460
and how to be with you

795
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,900
all my life!

796
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:58,780
You said

797
00:29:58,780 --> 00:30:00,370
that you wanted to be a good lawyer.

798
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:02,010
Fine.

799
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:04,540
After graduation,

800
00:30:05,370 --> 00:30:06,060
I gave up the postgraduate exam,

801
00:30:06,060 --> 00:30:07,010
I took cases with you,

802
00:30:07,010 --> 00:30:08,420
and established Chong&Wei.

803
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:10,060
But now you want me

804
00:30:10,060 --> 00:30:10,900
to give up my own career

805
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,180
just because you can't decide your work?

806
00:30:16,580 --> 00:30:17,180
Qian Wei,

807
00:30:18,330 --> 00:30:19,780
don't mix business with private life,

808
00:30:19,780 --> 00:30:20,460
all right?

809
00:30:21,940 --> 00:30:22,580
This isn't

810
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:24,370
as serious as you think it is.

811
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:26,610
When you can't pass
the National Bar Examination,

812
00:30:27,130 --> 00:30:27,730
you'll never have a chance

813
00:30:27,730 --> 00:30:28,900
to be promoted.

814
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:30,370
If you can

815
00:30:30,370 --> 00:30:31,610
exchange a job with 6,000 yuan a month

816
00:30:31,610 --> 00:30:33,300
for some shares worth 100 million,

817
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:34,330
why don't you do that?

818
00:30:36,420 --> 00:30:37,700
Why don't you?

819
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:39,490
It should

820
00:30:39,490 --> 00:30:40,180
belong to us.

821
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:41,540
To you and me.

822
00:30:42,850 --> 00:30:43,460
Now,

823
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:44,540
you're a mere paralegal.

824
00:30:45,130 --> 00:30:45,940
So what?

825
00:30:46,010 --> 00:30:47,180
I'll be a lawyer!

826
00:30:56,250 --> 00:30:57,210
Time's up.

827
00:30:57,210 --> 00:30:57,940
You're overrunning the time.

828
00:30:59,730 --> 00:31:00,820
If you still want a conversation

829
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:01,700
with my paralegal,

830
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:03,300
make an appointment with me in advance.

831
00:31:04,250 --> 00:31:05,540
But you'd better do it

832
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:06,300
after we win the Morris case.

833
00:31:09,970 --> 00:31:10,490
There's something

834
00:31:10,490 --> 00:31:11,850
you'd better make clear today.

835
00:31:12,610 --> 00:31:14,010
From this day on,

836
00:31:14,010 --> 00:31:16,060
you and Lan He will be together.

837
00:31:16,850 --> 00:31:18,130
Lu Xun and I will be together.

838
00:31:24,540 --> 00:31:25,580
Why don't I know that?

839
00:31:26,130 --> 00:31:26,940
I mean at work.

840
00:31:29,610 --> 00:31:30,460
Fine.

841
00:31:33,660 --> 00:31:35,130
Showing off your power, huh?

842
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:37,490
You even bought shoes there.

843
00:31:37,490 --> 00:31:38,820
Do you think it made you cool?

844
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:40,210
Shoes, huh?

845
00:31:40,730 --> 00:31:41,370
I...

846
00:31:41,370 --> 00:31:42,820
I never like high-heeled shoes.

847
00:32:18,060 --> 00:32:19,540
I want you to wipe the bag with it.

848
00:32:20,090 --> 00:32:21,130
The exhibits are in it.

849
00:32:22,060 --> 00:32:22,900
What a man!

850
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,460
I worked for you for four years.

851
00:32:24,460 --> 00:32:25,370
Couldn't you even

852
00:32:25,370 --> 00:32:26,490
defend me once

853
00:32:26,490 --> 00:32:27,700
in front of my ex-boyfriend?

854
00:32:27,700 --> 00:32:28,940
You protected the exhibits
instead of me.

855
00:32:28,940 --> 00:32:29,460
You know what?

856
00:32:29,460 --> 00:32:30,700
If I were drowned

857
00:32:30,700 --> 00:32:31,730
or electrocuted

858
00:32:31,730 --> 00:32:32,490
and became a ghost,

859
00:32:32,490 --> 00:32:33,780
I would haunt you.

860
00:32:34,010 --> 00:32:35,010
I'm your boss,

861
00:32:35,010 --> 00:32:36,490
not your boyfriend.

862
00:32:36,490 --> 00:32:37,820
I have no obligation to save you.

863
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,400
(Big Sister Liu)

864
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:46,460
(How is it going?)

865
00:32:46,460 --> 00:32:47,490
(Are you getting back together?)

866
00:32:52,010 --> 00:32:52,700
(Not at all.)

867
00:32:53,370 --> 00:32:55,210
(Big Sister Liu)
(I'll work overtime with Lu Xun until I die.)

868
00:32:58,010 --> 00:32:58,580
